get.summary: Get list of plan types based on search criteria
get.description: Returns a list of plan types based on search criteria.

parameters.name: county_code
parameters.description: County code (5 digit FIPS code). This will filter down to only plan types in the service area related to this county.

200.description: An array of Plan Type objects

count.description: Count representing the number of objects returned in the results array

next.description: query identifier defined by the api developer for getting the next set of records

previous.description: query identifier defined by the api developer for getting the previous set of records
